    "Future work should focus on leveraging LLMs to solve more complex optimization problems by exploring approaches such as interpreting LLM behavior and comprehensively evaluating performance on diverse issues.",
    "The exploration of enhancing LLMs with EAs is still in its early and fragmented stages.",
    "Areas beyond prompt engineering and NAS deserve further in-depth and systematic investigation.",
    "These endeavors are crucial in advancing Evolutionary Computing to effectively address the forefront challenges in the AI community.",
    "Theoretical analysis of algorithms combining LLMs and EAs from an optimization theory perspective is essential to understand properties like convergence and complexity."
